    "The checklist's scope, targeting various stakeholders including researchers, clinicians, editors, peer reviewers, and authors, positions CHEER as a versatile tool with far-reaching implications.",
    "The methodology, drawing from the EQUATOR guidelines, ensures a rigorous and evidence-based approach, further solidifying the credibility of CHEER.",
    "The outlined plan for the dissemination and promotion of CHEER demonstrates a comprehensive strategy to ensure a widespread adoption of the reporting guidelines.",
    "By involving authors of medical research papers, collecting feedback, and actively engaging with journals, the CHEER project aims to integrate the checklist seamlessly into the publication process.",
    "The creation of a dedicated website further emphasizes the commitment to transparency and continuous improvement."
